I kind of came in with Laura Mulvey's

01:02:00.630 --> 01:02:02.440
Visual Pleasure and Narrative Cinema.

01:02:02.440 --> 01:02:07.440
So the idea of visual
pleasure and aesthetics

01:02:08.060 --> 01:02:13.020
