01:07:31.210 --> 01:07:36.210
- Yeah, some of the things
that have struck me here

01:07:37.880 --> 01:07:42.880
is Kathleen talking
about this idea of desire

01:07:44.250 --> 01:07:48.510
and Marla talking about
